        "tau_s",
        "reabs"
      ],
      "docstring": "Realistic for a deep trap (E_rec = 359 nK << ODT depth ~uK): the recoiled atom\ndoes NOT leave - it stays, thermalises, and HEATS the cloud, melting the (~22%)\ncondensate. Closed form from the trapped-Bose-gas energy E(T)=A T^4 below Tc,\nA = 3(zeta4/zeta3) kB/Tc^3; condensate number N0(s) = Ntot[1-(T/Tc)^3]."
    },
